vidoeTitle: Govt will apply “extreme caution” to easing lockdown  - BBC News
description: The government has said it will exercise "extreme caution" over lifting the lockdown. Ministers stress it will be a gradual process, not a single leap to freedom.

vidoeTitle: Russia swaps Victory Day parade for air show - BBC News
description: Russia's Victory Day parade has been cancelled because of the coronavirus pandemic, but in neighbouring Belarus the parade went ahead as planned.
